Together, we made something we proudly call Dance On. A place where we can express ourself as a dancer. I was chosen to be the main cast of Dance On 2, It was truly a joy, an honour, and one of my best memories. I remember bursted into tears before go on the stage overwhelmed with all the feelings :') .

I never regret a decision to join LSPR Dance because I have learned many things such as how to be a responsible, dicipline, meticulous, proffesional, etc. But, the best thing is the people. It is full of incredible, hardworking, talented people who have a beautiful heart that sincerely loving each other. Thankyou, I love you, and I adore each of you.
.
This post is a dedication to all the casts and crews of dance on 3. D-11 everybody! Keep the spirit and always stay together. LSPR dance will always magically nail every performances. 
GOOD LUCK AND GOD SPEED 💞

If you guys want to catch their performance, Dance On 3 : Move In Diversity, check @lsprdance and don't hesitate to buy the tickets. Your eyes will be on stalks! 👀

Yesterday, me and the other finalists had a chance to visit Setu Babakan, the center of the Betawi Cultural Village. I was very impressed because they preserve the Betawi culture well. There are a spot for fishing, watercycle, wagon, and also lake-view cycling. You can also try Betawi's traditional food along the road. 
But for me, what makes it even more beautiful is the people. We are warmly welcomed. They showed us traditional dance and even told us how to make kerak telor!
.
Thankyou Setu Babakan 💕
.
.

I (A WORD, BIGGER AND DEEPER THAN LOVE) YOU
.
Tanpa orang orang ini, pasti ga mungkin bisa sampe di saat ini dengan keadaan ini
.
Makasih buat rasa sayang, rasa percaya, dan dukungan kalian semua dari awal proses
.
Makasih udah nemenin audisi, bantuin belajar, bantuin tanya jawab, ngasih masukkan, koreksi. Makasih udah mau minjemin ini itu, gojekkin ini itu tengah malem sekalipun, mau ngajarin nandak, makasih udah ngerjain tugas kampus gua yang terteter, makasih buat segala tulisan, vn, foto dan vidio motivasi yang ga pernah berhenti, makasih buat kalimat penyemangat dan motivasi setiap ketemu, yang ga tau lagi berapa banyak, makasih udah meluangkan waktunya untuk membantu gua. Makasih buat suara kalian, sumpah suara kalianlah yang bikin gua percaya diri dan tersenyum selama di atas panggung. Makasih atas tetek bengek yang kalian bawa buat gua. Disaat gua dipanggil maju, makasih udah ikut terharu dan bangga. Bener bener makasih banyak banget sama semua semua yang udah kalian lakukan. Bener bener makasih, padahal udah banyak janji yang gua ingkari, ga ngasih waktu untuk kalian, dan ga ada disaat kalian butuh, tapi kalian tetep pol pol an :(
.

Bener bener merasa beruntung dan diberkati banget punya kalian di hidup ini. Kalianlah yang menjadi motivasi gua untuk melakukan yang terbaik, karena udah banyak pengorbanan dan bantuan yang kalian kasih, ga mau bikin itu sia-sia
.
.
